```mermaid
%%{init: {"theme": "base", "themeVariables": {"fontSize": "18px", "primaryTextColor": "#111111", "secondaryTextColor": "#111111", "tertiaryTextColor": "#111111", "textColor": "#111111", "lineColor": "#616161"}}}%%
